To cite briard in publications, please use:

Fenner, M. (2021). Briard: a Ruby library for conversion of DOI Metadata.
DataCite.

A BibTeX entry for briard is

@misc{fenner_2021,
  url = {https://github.com/front-matter/briard},
  author = {Fenner, Martin},
  keywords = {doi, metadata, crossref, datacite, schema.org, bibtex, codemeta},
  title = {Briard: a Ruby library for conversion of DOI Metadata},
  publisher = {Front Matter},
  note = {Ruby gem and command-line utility for conversion of DOI metadata from and to different metadata formats, including schema.org.},
  year = {2021}
}
